// .cursorrules im Root
// Globale Instructions die IMMER gelten

Code Style:
- TypeScript strict mode
- Tailwind for styling (no custom CSS unless needed)
- Component structure: /components/[name]/[Name].tsx

Design Principles:
- Professional, not startup-y
- Clean borders over shadows
- Consistent spacing (multiples of 4px)
- Mobile-first responsive

Colors (always use):
- Primary: #0052A3
- Primary Hover: #003D7A
- Borders: #e5e7eb
- Text: #1a1a1a (headers), #374151 (body)

Never:
- Use emojis in professional UI
- Add unnecessary animations
- Overcomplicate simple tasks